Ik sluit alles af.

423
00:29:59.360 --> 00:30:00.850
Oké. schat.

424
00:30:03.120 --> 00:30:04.645
Welterusten. mam.

425
00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:06.610
Welterusten. schat.

426
